# Google ADK Tutorial 11: Built-in Tools & Grounding
# Environment variables for grounding agent

# Choose ONE of the following authentication methods:

# Method 1: Gemini API (AI Studio) - Free tier available
# Get your API key at: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
GOOGLE_API_KEY=your_api_key_here

# Method 2: VertexAI (Google Cloud) - For production use
# GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS=/path/to/your/service-account.json
# GOOGLE_CLOUD_PROJECT=your_project_id
# GOOGLE_CLOUD_LOCATION=us-central1

# Optional: Force VertexAI API (required for maps grounding)
# GOOGLE_GENAI_USE_VERTEXAI=1